{"tid":578332,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"點解日系game中文化會積極過歐美game?","createTime":"2018-03-02T13:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T09:33:09.000Z","uid":80323,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f4e6205e294e1a24512e8a5d0eca2f9815ce16b1","tid":578332,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T13:57:42.000Z","msg":"而加日系game絕大部份都有中文版，三國無雙、少女與戰車、刀劍神域、新次元遊戲、無夜國度、偶像大師、伊蘇、tales等等日系game全部都有<br />\n<br />\n但係歐美game就有D無中文版，kingdom come deliverance, mass effect andromeda, Dirt, just cause 3, hitman同batman arkham knight都無中文版，hitman直情無係港服賣<br />\n<br />\n係咪因為game廠覺得香港人鍾意日系game同日漫，唔鍾意歐美game，所以日系game就積極出中文版，歐美game就唔出咁多?"},{"pid":"b9f49b199a78442f97f414da1eb596198c90b3c1","tid":578332,"uid":71237,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T14:03:56.000Z","msg":"日本market細過歐美market<br />\n所以日本廠商咪積極啲搞中文化"},{"pid":"4b313dff1a0021f0fb21c02672f72df960d592da","tid":578332,"uid":149607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T14:06:09.000Z","msg":"亞洲遊戲中文化是常識吧"},{"pid":"b49b46b743320aaaa3a568afa06b491d59a63907","tid":578332,"uid":8659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T14:07:48.000Z","msg":"起底啊"},{"pid":"ee17c439ffc0e92bdaa3fb8197115ad7f6c87ebf","tid":578332,"uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T14:12:00.000Z","msg":"你理閪得人 <br />\ncrysis有中文化已經贏日系九條街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9cb6681a514c16ccfbc3bff1c010692af636e3e","tid":578332,"uid":46933,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T14:14:49.000Z","msg":"日系爛game根本係歐美無市場"},{"pid":"123e5331c10a77027a9ce6c57b6bb89572a9cdcd","tid":578332,"uid":26200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T14:29:49.000Z","msg":"英文係國際語言<br />\n日文唔係"},{"pid":"09d95add71740b538301b73f26b64befc188d1b9","tid":578332,"uid":128993,"like